@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam rectangleRoundCorner 8
skinparam rectangleFontSize 12

title Layer Types by Abstraction Level\nFrom concrete foundation to abstract presentation

rectangle "**Presentation Layer**\n//Most abstract - Most volatile//\nUI Components | View Models | Presentation Logic" as PRES #B3D9FF

rectangle "**Application Layer**\n//Use-case coordination//\nUse Cases | Workflows | App Services" as APP #CCE5CC

rectangle "**Domain Layer**\n//Business logic and rules//\nBusiness Rules | Domain Entities | Domain Services" as DOM #FFE0B2

rectangle "**Infrastructure Layer**\n//Technical services//\nPersistence | Messaging | Security" as INFRA #E0CFE8

rectangle "**Foundation Layer**\n//Most concrete - Most stable//\nUtilities | Platform Abstraction | Data Structures" as FOUND #F0D6D6

PRES -[#3366AA]-> APP
APP -[#3366AA]-> DOM
DOM -[#3366AA]-> INFRA
INFRA -[#3366AA]-> FOUND

note right of PRES
  **Volatile:** Changes
  with user needs and
  UI technology
end note

note right of FOUND
  **Stable:** Rarely
  changes; reusable
  across applications
end note
@enduml
